  "title": "KeepEquipped",
  "description": "Keep your armor and items in your hands when you die.",
  "body": "<div align=\"center\">\n<h1>KeepEquipped</h1>\n<a href=\"https://fabricmc.net\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Mod%20Loader-Fabric-lightyellow?logo=data:image/png;base64,\"></a>\n<img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Enviroment-Server-purple\">\n</div>\n<hr/>\n\n![ ](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/d33bdb088a00bd742031398ca247c01d289811b9.png)\n<hr/>\n\n### Description\nThis Minecraft mod ensures that your equipped armor and the items in your main and off-hand are saved when you die, reducing the typical punishment of losing your gear. <br/> Make your Minecraft experience more forgiving while keeping the challenge alive!\n\n\n### Features:\n\n*   Save armor, offhand, and mainhand item\n*   Optionally degrade the durability of saved items\n*   Option to save all items on the hotbar\n*   Option to save all or a portion of the player's experience (Version 1.07+)\n*   Trinkets mod support (Version 1.10+t)\n\n\n### Modpack Permission:<br/>\nFeel free to use it in any modpacks.\n\n\n",
